# Project Overview - Mubashir Hassan Personal Website

This is a minimal, clean personal website showcasing Mubashir Hassan's work as a Tech Lead and full-stack developer.

## Tech Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 15 with React 19
- **Language**: TypeScript
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS v4
- **Components**: Custom component system with CVA variants
- **Utilities**: clsx + tailwind-merge

## Design Philosophy
Inspired by leerob.com, following minimal design principles:
- Clean typography and generous whitespace
- Neutral color palette (light/dark mode support)
- Content-first, distraction-free layout
- Mobile-responsive design

## Key Files
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main homepage
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with metadata
- [lib/metadata.ts](mdc:lib/metadata.ts) - Site metadata configuration
- [lib/utils.ts](mdc:lib/utils.ts) - Utility functions including cn()

## Architecture Principles
- Component-based with modular, reusable components
- Type-safe with full TypeScript support
- Modern React 19 patterns (no forwardRef needed)
- Performance optimized for Core Web Vitals
